'''[[idea]] [[virus]]''' (''plural:'' '''[[idea viruses]]''' ''or'' '''idea virii''' (''non-standard''))

# {{cattag|Philosophy}}: A [[concept]] which is transmitted between people via networks (especially the Internet) generally without the knowledge or consent of the originator.  Results may range from nothing noticeable to the creation of new companies or products. Each new person generally modifies the idea before passing it on.